Linguistic Field(s): General Linguistics 

Subject Language(s): Yoruba (yor)

Language Family(ies): Niger-Congo 

Call Deadline: 16-Oct-2006 

Meeting Description:

Theme of the Conference: Yoruba Science and Technology. 

Yoruba Studies Association

Department of Linguistics and African Languages,
University of Ibadan, 
Ibadan, Nigeria.

2006 Annual National Conference
7th - 10th November 2006

Call for Papers:

All members and interested scholars of Yoruba Studies and allied disciplines are
hereby invited to participate and present papers in this year's Annual National
Conference of Yoruba Studies Association of Nigeria (YSAN) holding at the
University of Ibadan, Ibadan, Nigeria.

Sub-Themes:
-	Yoruba food technology
-	Yoruba metallurgy
-	Yoruba science and security
-	Yoruba Medicine
-	Yoruba textile technology
-	Yoruba wood technology
-	Yoruba agricultural technology
-	Yoruba dyeing technology
-	Yoruba brewery technology
-	Yoruba traditional science
-	Yoruba phamacognosy/ pharmacology
-	Yoruba science and technology in Education
-	Literature and Yoruba Science
-	Language and Yoruba Science
-	Literature and Yoruba Technology
-	Language and Yoruba Technology
-	Philosophy and Yoruba Science
-	Philosophy and Yoruba Technology
-	Yoruba calculus
-	Yoruba Metaphysics

